172.31.0.255

5 reserved IPs in a subnet:
10.0.0.0: Network address, 
10.0.0.1: Reserved for the VPC router in AWS, 
10.0.0.2: Reserved by AWS for DNS, 
10.0.0.3: Reserved for future use, and 
10.0.0.255: Broadcast address
